vote.title: Authorize an amendment to an existing lease agreement with Central Congressional Church to extend the lease agreement for an additional 25 years for approximately 20,000 square feet of land located at 5600 Royal Lane, to be used as a parking lot for the period September 25, 2024 through September 24, 2049 - Not to exceed $91,576.50 - Financing: General Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
